overview: The hit show that made waves all over Estonia is back on the screen! Ten people who claim to have psychic abilities are tested with various tasks right in front of the television viewers. Whether it's finding a missing person, describing what happened at a crime scene, or something even more crazy, the contestants can only rely on their extraordinary abilities. The performance of these incredible tasks is monitored by Estonia's leading skeptics and experts, including academics, criminalists, celebrities and investigative journalists. Their task is to exclude any fraud and collusion. At the end of each part, the sensitive with the fewest points must leave the competition.
